# Non-deterministic test artifacts: tests in test/services/test_video.py
# round-trip a still image through the still→video pipeline, producing
# *.png.mp4 outputs whose binary differs every run (mp4 container
# timestamps in headers). They should not be tracked.
test/resources/*.png.mp4